title: Personal Social Services: Staff of Social Services Departments, England
description: This report contains information on 112,200 jobs for people employed (directly and indirectly) by local authority adult social services departments in England
datasetNotes: Data can be found on the landing page by clicking on the link under latest version.  2 x XLS Spreadsheets and 1 CSV file can be found under Resources
sizingNotes: A large number of complex tables which will require some thought about dimensions.  The dataset may be better suited to the labour market family.
notes: This data set is concerned with the employment of people employed by LA socal services departments in England and may therefore sit better within the labour market family.
